entries.title: Jonathan Figoli - HappySad Episod | ft. Ludwig Ahgren
entries.description:
HappySad Episod - Ludwig Ahgren Streaming outro song 
How I made this song ⭐️ https://www.instagram.com/jfigoli

Music by : Jonathan Figoli ⭐️ http://jfigoli.fr
 
‼️FOLLOW ME & STAY TUNED, I WILL POST NEW BANGER 💥 SONGS SOON‼️

Subscribe on Spotify
⭐️https://open.spotify.com/artist/0g9pHMbweHfNfjQFAFfewx?si=msmMAEMbRf20MOyr-EYzrg 
Follow me on instagram
⭐️ http://jfigoli.fr
Add me on Facebook 
⭐️ https://www.facebook.com/jfigoli
Follow me on youtube 
⭐️ https://www.youtube.com/user/vilcanara
Visit my Website
⭐️ http://jfigoli.fr


Lyrics & Vocal : Ludwig Ahgren 
WATCH LUDWIG LIVE 
⭐️ https://www.twitch.tv/ludwig
follow on twitter 
⭐️ https://www.twitter.com/ludwigahgren
follow on instagram 
⭐️ https://www.instagram.com/ludwigahgren
join his subreddit 
⭐️ https://old.reddit.com/r/LudwigAhgren/
WATCH his Youtube
⭐️ https://www.youtube.com/c/Ludwigahgren

Arranger : Nicolas Martinez
⭐️ https://instagram.com/niko_huko

Mastering : Melancholy Studios 
⭐️ https://www.facebook.com/melancholystudios


❤️ THANK YOU LUDWIG! ❤️ Thanks for hiring me to write this song for the Ludwig Ahgren Streaming outro and for all the new listeners I've received due to all of this, for...everything. I' m making music for different style video games, commercials, movies, shorts and now outro of the famous Ludwig Ahgren Streamer! ❤️. 
Thank you just isn't enough to express my appreciation. Please go have fun and enjoy HappySad episod with Lud and me. 🙏❤️
‼️Stay tuned, I decide now to post my songs!
I can tell you that some new banger 💥 songs will coming soon‼️
Original soundtracks From different video games projects, Epic music, electro, Orchestral, ambiances, funny, hip hop, French style songs...

Love, 
Jonathan


HappySad Episod, Full Track available on Spotify : 
⭐️ https://open.spotify.com/track/1ViYjxrZtQCutiInnHF32e

🎵 If you need music or sound design for your project, contact me. 🎵
⭐️ jofigoli@gmail.com


⚡️Please help me out and buy or stream the song! Ripping the song from YouTube to mp3 hurts the little guys like me just trying to make a career in music and make enough money to rent an apartment and pay our bills. Thank you so much!💕

entries.title: Hyper Potions - Friends (Sonic Mania Opening Animation Song)
entries.description:
❤️  If you want to help us recover lost income from all our shows being cancelled this year, we'd appreciate anything! Thank you!!! - http://PayPal.me/KevinandIan

❤️ THANK YOU SEGA! ❤️ Thanks for hiring us to write the cinematic music for the Sonic Mania trailers, for all the new listeners we've received due to all of this, for...everything. This song is a thank you to all of our friends we're meeting on this journey. We were just 2 friends making music together, hanging out and playing games and now we're involved with amazing projects like Sonic Mania. Thank you just isn't enough to express our appreciation. Please go have fun and enjoy Sonic Mania with us. ALSO, huge thank you to Paramount and SEGA for using Friends in the Sonic Movie, incredibly grateful to have a song in a movie. 😌🙏❤️

Yeah...we still can’t believe this song is actually in the Sonic Movie, THE SONIC THE HEDGEHOG MOVIE 😮😮😮😮

Love, 
Ian and Kevin

⭐ Buy/Stream: https://fanlink.to/sonicmaniafriends ⭐

*Please help us out and buy or stream the song! Ripping the song from YouTube to mp3 hurts the little guys like us just trying to make a career in music and make enough money to rent an apartment and pay our bills. Thank you so much!

❤️ Help us by buying some merch! ❤️
